               <seg corresp="#KR3c0001_tls_001-146a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T21:16:33.526+09:00">The laws and regulations</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3c0001_tls_001-146a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T21:17:36.76+09:00">are the standards of behaviour of the myriad people.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3c0001_tls_001-211a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T21:19:25.225+09:00">The enlightened ruler, inside his state, puts into practice his laws and regulations/system of administrative procedures</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3c0001_tls_015-115a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T21:28:40.914+09:00">Laws and regulations</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3c0001_tls_015-115a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T21:28:41.343+09:00">are the means by which the ruler organises the realm and prevents wickedness.</seg>
